{"id": 237079558, "title": "Lalu Prasad reaffirms calls for nationwide caste census, says \u2018huge\u2019 income gaps in India", "text": "Citing World Inequality Lab\u2019s latest working paper on caste-based income disparities, Rashtriya Janata Dal (RJD) chief Lalu Prasad Yadav Monday renewed calls for a nationwide caste census \u2014 a development that comes as Opposition pressure mounts on the Centre to deliver on the contentious issue. In a post on X, Yadav quoted a World Inequality Lab paper. The paper showed that general castes had 88.4 percent of India\u2019s total national income in 2022 while OBC and Scheduled Castes had only 9 and 2.6 percent, respectively. It also said that there were no billionaires among India\u2019s Scheduled Tribes.", "summary": "", "url": "https://indianexpress.com/article/india/lalu-prasad-reaffirms-calls-for-nationwide-caste-census-says-huge-income-gaps-in-india-9398506/", "image": "https://images.indianexpress.com/2024/06/Lalu-Yadav.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-18 00:00:44", "author": null, "language": "en", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": -0.861}